<h1 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:24px;color:#1a1a2e;text-align:center;font-weight:700;">Your Invoice</h1>
<p style="text-align:center;color:#6b7280;margin:0 0 24px;">Hello {{firstName}}, please find attached the invoice for order <strong>{{orderNumber}}</strong>.</p>

<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:0 0 24px;background:#f8f7f4;border-radius:12px;">
  <tr><td style="padding:16px 20px;">
